Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:05.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}深呼出一两口气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:08.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}站起来吧拳击手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:12.11,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}起死回生的机会只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:15.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}敲响画中的门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:19.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}花落暗香留
